if I need more help, okay?

917
00:54:08,875 --> 00:54:09,875
Ratnamala!

918
00:54:12,541 --> 00:54:13,625
(Hindi) Get in the car.

919
00:54:14,125 --> 00:54:15,250
(Hindi) I want to go home.

920
00:54:15,375 --> 00:54:16,375
By bus.

921
00:54:17,291 --> 00:54:18,625
That's where I'm headed too!

922
00:54:25,750 --> 00:54:28,000
Good freaking grief!

923
00:54:35,750 --> 00:54:38,166
Hey lady... It doesn't look like
you're going home.

924
00:54:38,291 --> 00:54:39,291
(Hindi) I want to go home!

925
00:54:39,875 --> 00:54:41,875
You'd dare marry another girl
and bring her here?

926
00:54:43,375 --> 00:54:44,541
I'll kill you!

927
00:54:56,125 --> 00:54:57,541
